NuxCPSCollector

The goal of Collector Document is to create thrue the web an html form
with many kind of fields input like string, email, date, selection, 
radio, ... and let the Collector Document make the validation and error
handling. 
The action taken by the CollectorDocument is to store the data into 
CollectorItem that can be exported.

You can modify the Form (add edit move delete fields) at any time without
loosing already collected data.
You can configure the message displayed after a valid submission.
You can show statistic on data collected after a submission.
You can limit the number of submission per user to one.
You can display to the user his latest valid data submitted.
You can download all data collected as csv file.
